{"tid":962883,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［準備破處］倪晨曦宣布封盤　公開男友驚喜求婚細節︰佢好似識穿越一樣","createTime":"2018-12-31T08:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T09:45:32.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fff07c6bb10523e4e96d6c5899b159924f6676be","tid":962883,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T08:06:36.000Z","msg":"2018年的最後一天，又有喜訊，就係倪晨曦（Elva）在IG公開男朋友「V先生」的求婚短片，正式宣布已與圈外男朋友訂婚，女神封盤了！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MMKNjbB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMMKNjbB.png&h=3ee613a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/31/160559_f901b40bfbdc938bca2cf60935ef785b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F31%2F160559_f901b40bfbdc938bca2cf60935ef785b.png&h=f6b5e097&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/31/160603_d005bbf6d3c8d72492f6cb31170d7012.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F31%2F160603_d005bbf6d3c8d72492f6cb31170d7012.png&h=46110eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/31/160605_686eba4cec6215ee56458da4e42bda24.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F31%2F160605_686eba4cec6215ee56458da4e42bda24.png&h=bc264ef1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/31/160608_a8bc2332fa494ca0952c0d6e63205504.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F31%2F160608_a8bc2332fa494ca0952c0d6e63205504.png&h=5e96fd34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「我想了很久很久，這件事是人生中那麼重要的時刻，也是今年讓我感觸最深的一件事，想要分享給你們，那就是我訂婚了！」Elva在IG寫了半百字感言，交代男友求婚的始末和感受。她說男朋友是在巴黎時裝周期間求婚的，還夾埋髮型師一齊給她驚喜，騙她說銀包不見了，當她回頭去找銀包的時候，原本應該在香港的男朋友竟然突然出現在眼前，她笑言還以為他「穿越」了！<br />\n<br />\n在求婚短片中，只見V先生說了一堆說話，然後Elva又笑又哭，「他說了好多好多但我都不記得了，只是一個勁的哭，因為我好感動！！」Elva仲將男友讚到「天上有，地下無」，大家準備好黑超，因為真係勁閃：「沒有想過他會選擇在我覺得最浪漫的城市向我求婚，我們在一起也很少討論關於結婚的事，因為他知道我太愛工作了他總是默默的在我身邊不斷的付出，給我一個溫暖的避風港，這個全世界對我最好的男人，永遠都把我放在他前面，包容我照顧我，對自己總是超級節省，但把最好的都留給我，上輩子一定是做了什麼好事，這輩子有這樣的疼愛，原來安定下來的心感覺是那麼的踏實。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/277130/倪晨曦宣布封盤-公開男友驚喜求婚細節-佢好似識穿越一樣\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F277130%2F%E5%80%AA%E6%99%A8%E6%9B%A6%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%B0%81%E7%9B%A4-%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E9%A9%9A%E5%96%9C%E6%B1%82%E5%A9%9A%E7%B4%B0%E7%AF%80-%E4%BD%A2%E5%A5%BD%E4%BC%BC%E8%AD%98%E7%A9%BF%E8%B6%8A%E4%B8%80%E6%A8%A3&d=CkZeMYszKo0ts%2FLqs7T89Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=54e11d57\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/277130/倪晨曦宣布封盤-公開男友驚喜求婚細節-佢好似識穿越一樣</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28a1c8b234ba751816f07a9b5c8ad7efc220d63","tid":962883,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T08:07:59.000Z","msg":"我地都想穿越<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0dc0dc41becacebe3a5f67258ba0ddf8341411","tid":962883,"uid":81150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T08:10:16.000Z","msg":"世界未日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a32f79f5a59a02f0b0c67740d44a46b253b4a19","tid":962883,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T08:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解佢同細妹話係孖生但唔